===2020 census===
As of the [[2020 United States census|2020 census]], there were 23 people, 11 households, and 6 families residing in the city. The median age was 52.5 years, and 8.7% of residents were under the age of 18. 13.0% of residents were under the age of 20; 8.7% were between the ages of 20 and 24; 8.7% were from 25 to 44; 52.2% were from 45 to 64; and 17.4% were 65 years of age or older. For every 100 females there were 91.7 males, and for every 100 females age 18 and over there were 90.9 males age 18 and over.<ref name="Census2020DP">{{cite web|title=2020 Decennial Census Demographic Profile (DP1)|url=https://api.census.gov/data/2020/dec/dp?get=NAME,DP1_0021P,DP1_0024P,DP1_0025C,DP1_0049C,DP1_0045C,DP1_0069C,DP1_0073C,DP1_0125P,DP1_0126P,DP1_0129P,DP1_0133P,DP1_0137P,DP1_0138P,DP1_0139P,DP1_0141P,DP1_0142P,DP1_0143P,DP1_0145P,DP1_0146P,DP1_0147C,DP1_0148C,DP1_0149C,DP1_0156C,DP1_0157C,DP1_0158C,DP1_0159P,DP1_0160P&for=place%3A06040&in=state%3A19|website=United States Census Bureau|year=2021|access-date=May 1, 2026|df=mdy}}</ref><ref name="Census2020PL">{{cite web|title=2020 Decennial Census Redistricting Data (Public Law 94-171)|url=https://api.census.gov/data/2020/dec/pl?get=NAME,P1_001N,P1_003N,P1_004N,P1_005N,P1_006N,P1_007N,P1_008N,P1_009N,P2_001N,P2_002N,H1_001N,H1_002N&for=place%3A06040&in=state%3A19|website=United States Census Bureau|year=2021|access-date=May 1, 2026|df=mdy}}</ref>

All residents lived in rural areas.<ref name="Census2020DHC">{{cite web|title=2020 Decennial Census Demographic and Housing Characteristics (DHC)|url=https://api.census.gov/data/2020/dec/dhc?get=NAME,P2_002N,P2_003N&for=place%3A06040&in=state%3A19|website=United States Census Bureau|year=2023|access-date=May 1, 2026|df=mdy}}</ref>

The [[population density]] was 114.0 inhabitants per square mile (44.0/km<sup>2</sup>). There were 11 housing units at an average density of 54.5 per square mile (21.0/km<sup>2</sup>), of which 0.0% were vacant. The homeowner vacancy rate was 0.0% and the rental vacancy rate was 0.0%.<ref name="Census2020DP"/>

Of the 11 households, 27.3% had children under the age of 18 living with them, 36.4% were [[Marriage|married-couple households]], 36.4% were cohabitating-couple households, 18.2% were households with a male householder and no spouse or partner present, and 9.1% were households with a female householder and no spouse or partner present. 45.5% of all households were non-families, 27.3% were made up of individuals, and 9.1% had someone living alone who was 65 years of age or older.<ref name="Census2020DP"/>

